snippet.title: A Million People Want Amber Out Of Aquaman 2 | Petition Keeps Growing in Numbers
snippet.description:
A petition shows that about a million people have decided that Amber Heard should not be in Aquaman 2. Johnny Depp Has been fired from Fantastic Beasts by WB and people believe his former wife should receive the same treatment. Check out the story here and share your comments down bellow #WarnerBros #JusticeforJohnny
